Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.60,default,,0,0,0,,I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:58.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 間違っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.60,default,,0,0,0,,I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:01.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真の敵は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:00:59.44,default,,0,0,0,,The real mastermind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.57,default,,0,0,0,,The director. It's that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長 あの男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:10.27,default,,0,0,0,,But the injured Kaiji\Nreluctantly put his arm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 満身創痍のカイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間に諭され
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.18,default,,0,0,0,,...after some persuasion\Nfrom his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しぶしぶ 矛を収める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:15.92,default,,0,0,0,,And his injuries were treated\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:15.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして とりあえずの止血を終える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと不格好ですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:19.87,default,,0,0,0,,It looks a bit strange, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… 行きましょう 病院に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:21.15,default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:23.69,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:26.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳 今なら くっつきますよ きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:26.16,default,,0,0,0,,They might still be able to\Nreattach your ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:29.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… みんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:28.90,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:37.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろいろ ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:37.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:35.40,default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:37.09,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんすか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これくらい当然ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.55,default,,0,0,0,,Come on. This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:44.41,default,,0,0,0,,We were delighted that you\Nwere able to take them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:44.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち本当に うれしかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:44.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一矢報いてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:49.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントですよ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:53.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.46,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:58.59,default,,0,0,0,,Then Kaiji went to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:02:00.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして カイジ 病院へと向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.12,default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.59,default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:07.47,default,,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引っかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.28,default,,0,0,0,,A thought struck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.66,default,,0,0,0,,Something came to Kaiji's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:15.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よぎる カイジに「何か」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.28,default,,0,0,0,,A plan to defeat the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長を倒しうる 「何か」が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.90,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Heresy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.32,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:48.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… カイジさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.88,default,,0,0,0,,Were you aware of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってた？ここ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.10,default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:57.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この横の入り口さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.55,default,,0,0,0,,The side opening\Nof this tissue box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.26,default,,0,0,0,,The side of the tissue box\Ncan be easily opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティッシュ箱の横が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなふうに あっさり開くこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:06.33,default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think I was aware,\Nbut then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:06.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ… 知ってたような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:06.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らなかったような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おたくは 何で知ってたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.58,default,,0,0,0,,How did you come to\Nknow about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:14.27,default,,0,0,0,,Well, when we needed\Nplenty of tissues urgently...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:14.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや… １度 急いでティッシュを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:14.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,配らなきゃならないときが あって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.49,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ そんなことでもないかぎり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通やらないって こんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:23.20,default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't realise this\Nif it weren't for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:29.76,default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't think out of the box,\Nyou won't notice a side opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:28.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:28.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この横の口は 通常の考えの外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず 気が付かない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:34.80,default,,0,0,0,,If we can take advantage\Nof this side opening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:36.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に この入り口をうまく使えば…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,裏を取れる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.86,default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.04,default,,0,0,0,,There might be a way to outwit\Nand defeat the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:41.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長を出し抜く突破口だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 隙間？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:54.07,default,,0,0,0,,A gap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.64,default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:58.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.78,default,,0,0,0,,It fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入る…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.35,default,,0,0,0,,It won't fall nor slip out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:11.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちない 外れないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.52,default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:20.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中で 引っ掛かってるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.86,default,,0,0,0,,It's held firmly inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:23.80,default,,0,0,0,,I can get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:26.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取れる 取れる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.43,default,,0,0,0,,I can get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取れる！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.13,default,,0,0,0,,I can get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.26,default,,0,0,0,,To think that the tissue box\Nwas made like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティッシュの箱が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな構造だったなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:38.00,default,,0,0,0,,The box was glued together\Nin a simple way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のり付けの簡素さと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:40.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱の横を閉じている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:40.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この部分の長さが短く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.77,default,,0,0,0,,The length of the flaps was\Nmuch longer than their width,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:44.61,default,,0,0,0,,so that even when closed,\Nthere is a gap in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:45.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,閉じたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:45.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに中央部に空間ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.29,default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately,\Ndue to these two factors,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この２つが幸いし…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:54.26,default,,0,0,0,,anything inserted from outside the\Nbox would emerge on the inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:52.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その結果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:52.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外の隙間から入れたものは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱の中で顔を出し
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り出すことができる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.80,default,,0,0,0,,and can then be taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.91,default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, since the gap\Nis very slight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも 隙間が僅かであるため
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.80,default,,0,0,0,,the inserted item would\Nnot slip out easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのものは そう簡単に外れない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 願ってもない構造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.42,default,,0,0,0,,This structure was a god-send!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:10.56,default,,0,0,0,,It's probably the\Nbest possible situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考え得る最高の状態と言っていい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.76,default,,0,0,0,,This is great...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.32,default,,0,0,0,,This box is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この箱は すげえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.46,default,,0,0,0,,But it's only\Nhalf of the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし これだけじゃ まだ半分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１つ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:27.33,default,,0,0,0,,There's something else.\NI need one more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１つ必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:32.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決定的な条件が あと１つ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.27,default,,0,0,0,,There is one other\Ncritical factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.27,default,,0,0,0,,It has to be in this toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このトイレに あって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.18,default,,0,0,0,,...and also on that floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのフロアにも ある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.00,default,,0,0,0,,Something that resembles\Npaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か 紙のようなもの…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:51.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ… 金は駄目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.02,default,,0,0,0,,Money wouldn't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:57.32,default,,0,0,0,,Something else...\NSomething different!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと 何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か 別の… 何か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ペーパータオル
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.03,default,,0,0,0,,Paper towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペーパータオル！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.36,default,,0,0,0,,Paper towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.18,default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じもの…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.76,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.18,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じものだ 利根川が使っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペーパータオルと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.17,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same paper towel\Nthat Tonegawa used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.82,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.78,default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.66,default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:36.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か… 誰か持ってないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:38.06,default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone has anything\NI can write with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か… 書くもの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ あの… ボールペンなら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:47.04,default,,0,0,0,,Is a ball pen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.02,default,,0,0,0,,I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道具が そろった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.41,default,,0,0,0,,I have all the tools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうの部屋にあるのと同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペーパータオル
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.29,default,,0,0,0,,The same paper towels\Nas in the opposite room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.33,default,,0,0,0,,A ball pen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボールペン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして あのティッシュ箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.42,default,,0,0,0,,...and the tissue box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.92,default,,0,0,0,,With these three things,\Nthe path will open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この３つがあれば 道が開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.93,default,,0,0,0,,That director can be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倒せる あの会長を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.80,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… それって一体？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.90,default,,0,0,0,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.62,default,,0,0,0,,When we go return\Nto the other room,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうに戻ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は あるギャンブルを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.42,default,,0,0,0,,I will propose a special gamble\Nwith the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長に申し込む
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.32,default,,0,0,0,,And that gamble will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのギャンブルは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじ引きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.32,default,,0,0,0,,A lottery!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.06,default,,0,0,0,,The lottery tickets are made\Nwith folded paper towels,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじは ペーパータオルの紙切れ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじ箱が 空のティッシュ箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.06,default,,0,0,0,,and the lottery box\Nwill be the tissue box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:52.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:52.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな ひしゃげたやつではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:54.07,default,,0,0,0,,Not a damaged one like this\Nof course, but a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未使用のものを使う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未使用のティッシュ箱は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒服に持ってきてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:58.07,default,,0,0,0,,One of the guys in black suits\Nwill bring a tissue box to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:03.09,default,,0,0,0,,And that box will be\Nopened in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして フロアで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,衆人環視の中 開封してもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:08.58,default,,0,0,0,,We'll place 50 or 60 pieces\Nof these lottery tickets in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:07.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに こんなくじを５０～６０枚入れ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その中に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:13.70,default,,0,0,0,,Only one of them\Nwill be marked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:15.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなふうに 印を付けた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:15.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじを１枚だけ入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:18.48,default,,0,0,0,,It's a gambling draw where the\None who gets this first, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを先に引いた方が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちっていう ギャンブルだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:23.69,default,,0,0,0,,This gamble is\Nnormally a test of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常 この手のギャンブルは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運否天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.87,default,,0,0,0,,Players normally do not\Ndraw the winning lot right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お互い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れくじを引き合うのが自然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:31.49,default,,0,0,0,,But I will draw it out easily\Non the first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:30.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが俺は それをあっさり引く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初っぱなに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:40.18,default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to say it, but\NI will have rigged the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのわけは 言わずもがな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕込んでおくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:46.61,default,,0,0,0,,I'll slip a fake winning ticket\Ninto all the boxes in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにあるティッシュ箱 全てに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:47.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偽りの当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.30,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.52,default,,0,0,0,,by placing the ticket into\Nthis gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も気付かないであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この横の入り口に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.00,default,,0,0,0,,prior to the gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前もって 当たりくじを入れておき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:01.56,default,,0,0,0,,And when my turn comes,\NI'll draw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを自分の番になったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:06.20,default,,0,0,0,,It will be a guaranteed win.\NSimple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで 必勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？ちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.82,default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.11,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それって イカサマですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:18.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不正ってことですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:18.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.06,default,,0,0,0,,It's dishonest, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.58,default,,0,0,0,,So what if it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.82,default,,0,0,0,,We must win this fight\Nno matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何としても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たなきゃいけない勝負に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.82,default,,0,0,0,,even if cheating\Nis what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマも くそも あるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.99,default,,0,0,0,,That's what they did\Nin the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうだって やってたことだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取る
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.07,default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure that I get\Nmy revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この耳のかたきは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちりと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.74,default,,0,0,0,,for this ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このかたきは 必ず取る
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.41,default,,0,0,0,,I will definitely\Nget revenge for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:56.32,default,,0,0,0,,What did they do anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:58.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… 何か やってたんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:58.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうも イカサマか何か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.14,default,,0,0,0,,Was it cheating or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,してたなんてもんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.29,default,,0,0,0,,It was much more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.33,default,,0,0,0,,They cheated right from the start,\Nup till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 最初から最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てイカサマ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:08.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでいた…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.69,default,,0,0,0,,I could have died...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:12.46,default,,0,0,0,,If I had made one wrong move,\NI would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一歩間違えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 死んでいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.81,default,,0,0,0,,They show no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつらは容赦しない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:21.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ イカサマでも 負けは負け
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:21.10,default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that they\Ncheated, it'd still be your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だまされる方が悪いと鼻で笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.45,default,,0,0,0,,They'd just sneer and\Nblame the one who lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっさり殺していた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.82,default,,0,0,0,,They kill people nonchalantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.58,default,,0,0,0,,I must win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つことだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.90,default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what I must do,\Nso long as it's a 100% win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手段を選ばず １００％勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.90,default,,0,0,0,,It's the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:46.04,default,,0,0,0,,This money is stained\Nwith everyone's blood:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金は 俺や石田さんや佐原…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:49.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの血で 真っ赤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.32,default,,0,0,0,,Mine, Ishida's and Sahara's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.88,default,,0,0,0,,Blood-stained money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血染めの金…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かけがえのない金…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.96,default,,0,0,0,,This is precious money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも やっぱり やめた方が…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.79,default,,0,0,0,,I still think that\Nit's better not to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:58.95,default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:02.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:02.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偽のくじを横から入れるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:02.73,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you place a fake\Nwinning lot in the side gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:06.26,default,,0,0,0,,the genuine lot\Nis still inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとは別に 正規の当たりくじも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入れますよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:08.26,default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:12.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし 会長が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:12.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に引くことになったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.76,default,,0,0,0,,What if the chairman were\Nto draw that out first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:17.17,default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to draw the winning\Nlot on the first try, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一発で引かれることも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるってことじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.56,default,,0,0,0,,There's only a 1 in 50 or\N1 in 60 chance of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５０分の１ ６０分の１って話だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:24.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも ０じゃないですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:24.41,default,,0,0,0,,But it's not zero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.63,default,,0,0,0,,There will definitely be risks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リスクは どうしたって出る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごみみたいな確率にびびって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.42,default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to give up\Nthis great opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この大チャンス 見送れるか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.65,default,,0,0,0,,...just because of\Nsuch a tiny risk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.76,default,,0,0,0,,No way I'll let this pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見送れるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:37.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも かけがえのない金って…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.89,default,,0,0,0,,But you said that\Nthis money was valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:41.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ そりゃそうだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.89,default,,0,0,0,,That is true too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 行くしかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.39,default,,0,0,0,,There is no other choice but to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:48.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くんだ 張るときなんだ 今は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.39,default,,0,0,0,,It's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.40,default,,0,0,0,,I'll stake everything on it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:51.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:51.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くしかねえって言ってんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.61,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.73,default,,0,0,0,,I said I have to, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それは いいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき 偽のくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.08,default,,0,0,0,,T-That's fine too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:58.37,default,,0,0,0,,You said you'd hide a ticket\Nin all of the boxes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部のティッシュに仕掛ける
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って言いましたよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱は 黒服に選ばせたいからな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:01.14,default,,0,0,0,,That's because I want the\Nblack suits to choose the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:05.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは 証拠が残りますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:04.57,default,,0,0,0,,That would mean leaving\Nsome evidence behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てのティッシュ箱に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじが残るのって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.80,default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't there be trouble\Nif they discover...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.98,default,,0,0,0,,...a winning ticket left in\Nall the tissue boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構やばいって言うか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.65,default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人 残す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.66,default,,0,0,0,,Someone will stay behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:23.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人 個室に残ってもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.16,default,,0,0,0,,Someone will stay behind here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 黒服が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティッシュ箱を持って行った後…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:27.71,default,,0,0,0,,And after the guy in a\Nblack suit choses a tissue box,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:34.91,default,,0,0,0,,he'll pull out the remaining lots\Nand flush them down the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残った当たりくじを抜いて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレに流す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:38.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ？これで問題ない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.56,default,,0,0,0,,Well? It won't be a problem then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの… 本当の当たりくじは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうするんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:42.85,default,,0,0,0,,What do we do with\Nthe real winning lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんが 偽の当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,横から持ってくるってことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:49.06,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you were to draw\Nthe fake winning lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の当たりくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.85,default,,0,0,0,,the genuine one would\Nstill remain inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:54.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱に残ることになりますよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.58,default,,0,0,0,,After you take out\Nthe winning ticket,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじを引いた後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.83,default,,0,0,0,,what happens\Nif they empty the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱を改められたら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てきちゃうじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:04.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１枚の当たりくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.94,default,,0,0,0,,They'll find the other ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ まずいっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん まずい まずい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.20,default,,0,0,0,,That would mean trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.55,default,,0,0,0,,- Not good at all...\N- Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だよ やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.53,default,,0,0,0,,It can't be done after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.08,default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.65,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かまわない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.50,default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.85,default,,0,0,0,,I'll bluff my way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごまかしうる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ごまかすって…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.84,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.29,default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳を貸せ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ そんなことで？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.56,default,,0,0,0,,You're going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.86,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:41.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で… でも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:41.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく 今は行くしかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.60,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.80,default,,0,0,0,,In any case,\NI have no other choice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来て 下がれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.74,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can go back\Nafter coming this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:49.75,default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely\Ntake down that demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倒す あの鬼を必ず
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわ… ざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより箱だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:54.36,default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Nbring all of the boxes here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってきてくれ 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.75,default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急ごう あんまり長く
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレにいるのは不自然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:02.48,default,,0,0,0,,Hurry. We'll arouse suspicion by\Nbeing in the toilet for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく見たら ティッシュ箱って…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:10.49,default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it, the front and back\Nof the tissue box looks the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前後一緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見た目が まるで対称…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.95,default,,0,0,0,,At first sight,\Nthey are almost identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:18.47,default,,0,0,0,,I won't know which side the\Nwinning ticket is placed in...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:19.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ 当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:19.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっち側に入れたか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.39,default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし これは すぐに解決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.66,default,,0,0,0,,However, it is solved at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:28.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱の底 下側が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.45,default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of the box\Nis different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは 下から見て頭側の部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.91,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji decides to\Nplace the ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:35.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちら側の側面に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:35.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじを仕込むことに決める
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:35.19,default,,0,0,0,,...in the left side of the box\Nwhen the bottom is facing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:38.93,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! There are more\Nover here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん こっちにも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくつか ありますけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.66,default,,0,0,0,,Bring them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.97,default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう 背の低い
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.91,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the shorter and more\Ncompressed tissue boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧縮タイプのティッシュ箱は…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メーカーによっては
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぴったりと のり付けがされ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.41,default,,0,0,0,,...are of a different brand\Nand more firmly glued together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.15,default,,0,0,0,,There is no gap for\Nthe ticket to be inserted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:00.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隙間ができず 入らない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちは無視
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.78,default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind those!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.67,default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.93,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:07.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 入り口から遠いその箱は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:07.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず持ってこない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:07.12,default,,0,0,0,,They're further from the entrance,\Nso they won't be brought in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.36,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:15.36,default,,0,0,0,,Thus while settling any\Nproblems that might be faced,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:15.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして 次々に湧き上がる疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:15.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題点を処理しつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.37,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji continues to insert\Nthe fake winning lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじの仕込みをこなす
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 残る当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,処分する係を１人残し 戻る
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:22.13,default,,0,0,0,,Then one from the group is\Nappointed to stay behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.87,default,,0,0,0,,...so as to destroy\Nthe remaining lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ名も知らぬ鬼のいるフロアへ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:33.40,default,,0,0,0,,They return to the room with the\Ndemon whose name remains unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざ 決戦の場へ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.38,default,,0,0,0,,Back to the final battleground!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,治療は大変だったのう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:48.83,default,,0,0,0,,It must have been tough\Npatching it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:54.05,default,,0,0,0,,However, as long as the\Nmoney is yours, all is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:54.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 金が入れば全てよし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ ２０００万円だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.57,default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:01.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目も くらむような大金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:01.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うれしいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.29,default,,0,0,0,,You must be delighted\Nat such a large sum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.93,default,,0,0,0,,...that's blinding to the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:04.08,default,,0,0,0,,Also, the pain you went through\Nmust surely add to the joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しかった分 喜びも ひとしお
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな中 やぼは言いたくないが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.58,default,,0,0,0,,I hate to ruin the fun,\Nbut...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.28,default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが カイジ様の今現在の債務額
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.54,default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:14.59,default,,0,0,0,,This is the debt you have\Naccumulated, Mr. Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.59,kaiji-Sign-top,,0,0,0,,[On 13th July\NMr. Kaiji]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:21.00,default,,0,0,0,,I might never get another\Nchance to reclaim this debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるときに返してもらわぬと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取りっぱぐれるのでな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.66,default,,0,0,0,,Well, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むなしくなってるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:36.13,default,,0,0,0,,It feels rather like I'll be going\Naway empty-handed from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりの実入りの少なさに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２０００万と言っても…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:44.08,default,,0,0,0,,It may be 20 million, but half\Nthe amount doesn't belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:44.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その内の半分の１０００万は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:44.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はなから俺の金じゃねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.28,default,,0,0,0,,In the end,\NI'm only getting 10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 俺の取り分は１０００万で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.63,default,,0,0,0,,After repaying this\Ndebt of 6.7 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:51.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この６７０万を返すと３００万の余り
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.59,default,,0,0,0,,I'll be left with only 3 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:54.48,default,,0,0,0,,And part of that would\Nbe spent on treating my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも 耳の治療で さらに減る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.56,default,,0,0,0,,And what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:58.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう それで？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が言いたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.80,default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１丁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.41,default,,0,0,0,,One more round...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:08.42,default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget the petty details\Nand have another match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:09.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けちなこと言わず もう一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.97,default,,0,0,0,,Match?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.24,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ終われない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は あんたと…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.34,default,,0,0,0,,It can't end like this.\NThis time, it'll be you and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.74,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mind your manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！無礼なことを言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあまあ 大目に見てやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:24.99,default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, let it go.\NHe doesn't seem to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:25.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は何も分かってないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが その気になれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.96,default,,0,0,0,,If I felt like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前なんぞ その日の内に 魚の餌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:33.80,default,,0,0,0,,I could turn you\Ninto fish bait in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:40.87,default,,0,0,0,,But a gentleman like me\Nwould never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が… わしは紳士だから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 そんなことは せんがね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感じないかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.91,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:51.10,default,,0,0,0,,Your winning streak has\Nreached its limit, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:49.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こよい カイジ君の勝ち運は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:49.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これがリミット
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:52.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上限だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.92,default,,0,0,0,,You've hit the maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上の勝ちは もう望めない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:57.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.86,default,,0,0,0,,I, who have seen\Nbloodshed before,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:01.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしのように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:01.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,修羅場をくぐってきた人間には
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.92,default,,0,0,0,,am aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いことは言わん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう やめた方がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:05.63,default,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything bad,\Nbut I'd advise you to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:10.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７００万払っても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:10.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１３００万残ればいいではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:10.82,default,,0,0,0,,After paying 7 million,\Nwon't you still have 13 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分 大金 御の字だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.63,default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge sum of money,\Nan astonishing amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！聞いてなかったのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.17,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Didn't you\Nhear what I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:19.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２０００万の内 半分は預かりの金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.72,default,,0,0,0,,Only half of that 20 million\Nis mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡す約束をした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.54,default,,0,0,0,,I made a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもん 破ればよかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.68,default,,0,0,0,,Won't it all work out\Nif you break that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.44,default,,0,0,0,,Go on and break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほご ほご
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな口約束 守る義務なし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:29.38,default,,0,0,0,,There is no reason\Nto keep a spoken promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばか言うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.14,default,,0,0,0,,What rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:36.08,default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're all fired up\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:36.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 今は一種の興奮状態だから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒロイックな気分で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,払うとか何とか言っておるが…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:40.32,default,,0,0,0,,You claim that you'll pay up\Nbased on heroic instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:45.43,default,,0,0,0,,But when back to your old routine,\Nyou'll recover your senses,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通の暮らしに戻れば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬く間に 普通の感覚に戻り…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:50.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通に裏切る それが人間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.64,default,,0,0,0,,and betray them in an instant! \NThat's only human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.40,default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:53.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！俺は裏切らない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.54,default,,0,0,0,,I won't betray them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ そういうことにしておこうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.40,default,,0,0,0,,Well, so be it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.54,default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference\Nto me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:02.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは どっちでも かまわんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:06.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:06.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.06,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.42,default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごまかして逃げるな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.55,default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to\Nworm your way out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺とやって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるのが怖いんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.16,default,,0,0,0,,You're just afraid\Nof losing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けて恥をかくのを恐れてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.43,default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of\Nthe shame from losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.50,default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう意味だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.43,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:23.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ わしがカイジ君に負けると
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:23.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恥なのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:23.17,default,,0,0,0,,Why should I feel ashamed\Nif I lost to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:27.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強者は相対的な意味で強者なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.96,default,,0,0,0,,Strength is relative, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一事一事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てに勝てるわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:30.68,default,,0,0,0,,There is no way to win\Nevery single battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:35.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いわゆる プロフェッショナルの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:35.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界を見ても そうじゃろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:34.55,default,,0,0,0,,That also applies to the\Nprofessional world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:39.15,default,,0,0,0,,Can a professional golfer beat\Nan amateur for every hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プロのゴルファーが アマとやって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ホール勝てるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１ホールだけに限れば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アマがプロを下すこともある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:44.89,default,,0,0,0,,The amateur could very well\Ndefeat the pro at a single hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たかが１度の負けを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恥だ うんぬん言うのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:48.50,default,,0,0,0,,Labelling that single defeat\Nas shameful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:52.63,default,,0,0,0,,...is a bad habit of\Nnarrow-minded folk like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:53.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君ら貧しき者の狭量 悪い癖だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.87,default,,0,0,0,,There's no shame about\Nsuch a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの 恥でも何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:20:00.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ… 二枚舌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:00.10,default,,0,0,0,,You two-headed snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.61,default,,0,0,0,,What about\NTonegawa just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきの利根川は どうなる？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:09.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき １度の負けを許さず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:09.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:08.08,default,,0,0,0,,Not only was he unpardoned\Non losing just one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:12.95,default,,0,0,0,,he was made to do\Nsomething so hideous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな すさまじいこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強いたじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い逃れだ こいつは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.92,default,,0,0,0,,That was just an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:19.32,default,,0,0,0,,He's heartless towards the\Nmistakes of his subordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部下の失態や敗北には苛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:23.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな拷問も辞さないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.53,default,,0,0,0,,and has no second thoughts\Nabout torturing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:26.40,default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to his turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の番になりそうになると
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巧妙に手のひらを返し
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごまかしてるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:30.20,default,,0,0,0,,he cleverly deceives\Nhis way out of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.36,default,,0,0,0,,How despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,卑劣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.88,default,,0,0,0,,He's the worst scum of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:36.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最高に醜悪な男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:40.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな… こんな男に比べれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:40.31,default,,0,0,0,,When compared with this man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでいった仲間 あるいは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.38,default,,0,0,0,,my companions who died,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.88,default,,0,0,0,,and Tonegawa who showed\Nhis willpower to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に意地を見せた利根川の方が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はるかに上だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.39,default,,0,0,0,,are all superior to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふわあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.38,default,,0,0,0,,This party has continued\Nway past midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーティーとはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜更かしが過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:58.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ これで…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.63,default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:01.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離さねえ もう一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.36,default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!\NOne more round!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:07.10,default,,0,0,0,,One more round;\NI don't care what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:07.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何としても もう一勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魑魅魍魎の世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:13.01,default,,0,0,0,,Hyodo, the monster who\Nrules the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:13.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに君臨する怪物 鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:17.41,default,,0,0,0,,After surrounding the bottom\Nof the pit with snares,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地の底で わなを巡らし… 今 挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.86,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji challenges him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.43,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Conditions.
